post_text:
A couple more solutions we are coming up with are: one delivery of lunch for the day and the next days breakfast. The breakfast will be cold or processed items you can warm in microwave. So please follow the food safety sheets that will be handed out tomorrow. Second if your children are not awake or not answering door, put a hamper or cooler outside the door that the delivery people can put the meal in instead of bringing it back to school or a telephone number so we can contact them . Today we had 20 some lunches come back because no one answered. But please follow the food safety sheets for these meals in hamper.
We will continue to evolve and try the best solutions possible for all our children.
Thanks for all the feedback we are trying our best and we will get through this.
Please share and we will be sending out more information

post_text: Ok so I was in HyVee getting some groceries, and I over heard some women talking about school lunch. The infamous its all that Michelle Obama. What most don't know so let me educate you. These nutritional changes that have been made have been planned since 96. Getting the details together is what took so long. Michelle can take the credit,because she was the one who pushed for more funding for fruits n veggies. So thanks to her she has given our kids a better choice in school lunches. So lets all encourage our kids to eat more fruits and veggies. I try everyday to make your children try new veggies. Fruits are never a problem. Just wanted to correct a little misinformation. #fruitsnveggies #michelleobama
